name: DLMM
description: $DLMM is a first of its kind Internet Capital Market project, built on the Solana blockchain, that focuses on generating revenue through the project treasury and then distributing those profits through a buyback and burn mechanism. These profits are earned by leveraging various cross-chain liquidity provision platforms in order to grow the token treasury. The initially focus will be using lower liquidity, higher APR methods such as Meteora's DLMM platform.
